{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-22","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 22","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada ćete raditi brze vežbe da proverite da li možete prepoznati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">d</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">t</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">n</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">l</span>.</p>\n<p>Ova reč opisuje čin potpuno samostalnog delovanja, bez bilo kakve pomoći od drugih.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk i dovrši reč ispod. Ispravni slogovi će biti zamenjeni kineskim znakovima.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Prva silaba koristi početak <span class=\"highlighted-text\">d</span> i jednostavan završetak <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, i ima drugi ton. Druga silaba koristi početak <span class=\"highlighted-text\">l</span> i jednostavan završetak <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>, i ima četvrti ton.</p>\n<p><ruby>独立<rp>(</rp><rt>dú lì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> To znači raditi stvari samostalno, bez pomoći drugih.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","lang":"zh-CN","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-22"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"独立 (dú lì)","feedback":"<p>Ova reč je sastavljena od dve sloga: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">dú</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lì</span>.</p>"}]},"inputType":"pinyin-to-hanzi","tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_initials.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":362.14,"fin